OL,3,CFrance becomes first country to
OL,4,Censhrine right to abortion in the
OL,5,Cconstitution
OL,7,FFrance has approved a bill to make
OL,8,Fwomen's right to abortion protected by
OL,9,Fthe French Constitution, on Monday.
OL,11,FThe bill was passed through in an
OL,12,Foverwhelming 780-72 vote, with nearly
OL,13,Fthe entire historic joint session at
OL,14,Fthe Palace of Versailles joining in a
OL,15,Flong standing ovation.
