OL,3,CFrance becomes first country to
OL,4,Censhrine right to abortion in the
OL,5,Cconstitution
OL,7,FThe policy was promised by the French
OL,8,Fpresident following a rollback of
OL,9,Fabortion rights by court rulings in
OL,10,Fthe United States.
OL,12,FIn June 2023, the decision by to strip
OL,13,Fwomen of the right to abortion
OL,14,Freverberated across Europe's political
OL,15,Flandscape.
OL,17,FIt forced the issue back into public
OL,18,Fdebate in France, at a time of
OL,19,Fpolitical upheaval.
