OL,3,CFrance becomes first country to
OL,4,Censhrine right to abortion in the
OL,5,Cconstitution
OL,7,FIn the lead up to the historic vote,
OL,8,FPrime Minister Gabriel Attal addressed
OL,9,Fthe 925 politicians gathered for the
OL,10,Fjoint session in Versailles.
OL,12,FHe called on them to make France a
OL,13,Fleader in women's rights and set an
OL,14,Fexample in defence of women's rights
OL,15,Ffor countries around the world.
OL,17,F"We have a moral debt to women," Attal
OL,18,Fsaid.
