OL,7,FHe paid tribute to Simone Veil, a
OL,8,Fprominent legislator, former health
OL,9,Fminister and key feminist who in 1975
OL,10,Fchampioned the bill that
OL,11,Fdecriminalised abortion in France.
OL,13,F"We have a chance to change history,"
OL,14,FAttal said in a moving and determined
OL,15,Fspeech.
OL,17,F"Make Simone Veil proud," he said to a
OL,18,Fstanding ovation.
OL,20,FThe right to an abortion has broad
OL,21,Fsupport among the French public.
