OL,7,FA recent poll showed support at over
OL,8,F80%, consistent with previous surveys.
OL,10,FThe same poll also showed that a solid
OL,11,Fmajority of people are in favour of
OL,12,Fenshrining it in the constitution.
OL,14,FThere were scenes of celebrations
OL,15,Faround France ahead of the historical
OL,16,Fjoint parliament session.
